code: @Override protected void deserializeBuffer(Buffer buffer) throws IOException {     deserializer.setNextBuffer(buffer).     while (deserializer.hasUnfinishedData()) {         RecordDeserializer.DeserializationResult result = deserializer.getNextRecord(record).         if (result.isFullRecord()) {             output.add(record.createCopy()).         }         if (result == RecordDeserializer.DeserializationResult.LAST_RECORD_FROM_BUFFER || result == RecordDeserializer.DeserializationResult.PARTIAL_RECORD) {             break.         }     } }
